title: Help Me Out

embed.description: I need to build a new computer so that i can finally begin work on my dream of making content. | Crowdfunding is a democratic way to support the fundraising needs of your community. Make a contribution today!

body: I'm going to keep this brief because everything you need to know can be learnt by clicking on the link. I love making people laugh and smile and I need people to help me do that.
